information on this and other BXA seminars call the Export Seminar Staff at</FONT></P>
<P ALIGN="center">
 <B><FONT FACE="Arial">(202) 482-6031</FONT></B><FONT FACE="Arial"> or the BXA Western Regional Office at </FONT><B><FONT FACE="Arial">(714) 660-0144</FONT></B><BR>
