<B>Welcome to CALSTART's User Forum!</B>

<BLOCKQUOTE><P>

CALSTART has streamlined its web site discussion groups into a single user forum where you can discuss advanced transportation topics of interest with other online users.  Want to post messages on NGVs, EVs, buy or sell vehicles or components, or simply discuss the latest advanced transportation news?  Just fill out the easy-to-use form below.  While reading messages, post new ones or reply to others using the available form links on every page.   For more info on CALSTART's User Forum, please read the <a href="faq.html">FAQ</a>.</P></BLOCKQUOTE>


