<DOCOLDNO>IA037-000725-B010-300</DOCOLDNO>
<DOCHDR>
http://www.calstart.org:80/about/pngv/pngv-0216.html 207.104.9.100 19970210060033 text/html 3413
HTTP/1.0 200 Document follows
Date: Mon, 10 Feb 1997 05:52:42 GMT
Server: NCSA/1.5.2
Content-type: text/html
