<h3>Southern Coalition for Advanced Transportation (SCAT)</h3><p>

<blockquote>
<B>Project Title:  Utility Van Conversions<p>
Performing Organization: Solar Car; Fisher Motors; Florida Power and Light, U.S. Electricar 
</B><p>

<P>POINT OF CONTACT: Bob Suggs 
<BR>
Telephone:  (305) 5224133<BR>


<P><B>Program Summary: </B></P> 

<P>Two utility vans manufactured by Utilimaster will be converted to electric for demonstration using the
Fisher/Saminco advanced electric drive packages. The vehicles will be placed in service in Florida
Power and Light's fleet. Training and O&M manuals will be provided</P>

<P><B>The Benefit: </B></P>

<P>Short haul military and urban cargo transport </P>

</blockquote>

