<TITLE> E-Mail Discussions- The Mountain Forum</TITLE>
</HEAD>
<BODY>
<!--E-Mail Discussions main page version 1.3 10/96 DTO--> 
<BODY background="/mtnforum/images/greyback.jpg" bgcolor="#c1e1f8" TEXT="#000000">
<LINK REV="made" HREF="mailto:mfsupport@mtnforum.org">
<TABLE BORDER=0  CELLPADDING=2  WIDTH=100%>
<TR>
 <TD COLSPAN=60 VALIGN=top>    
<img src="/mtnforum/images/mtnheader.jpg" alt="[Mtn-Forum logo]">
</TD>
<TD COLSPAN=120 VALIGN=TOP>
<img src="/mtnforum/images/mtnemaildiscuss.jpg" alt="[Mtn-Discussion logo]">
