<H2>Participant Background Information</H2>
<P>
For the rest of the questions in this survey, please check as many answers as apply, and write out any responses or additions as you wish.  If you are replying by e-mail, please indicate your choices by writing out the appropriate question number and letter(s)_that apply, and filling in the blanks.  All comments are welcome, and all answers are confidential.  Survey results will be made available in summary form only. <EM>For the multiple-entry boxes, please check one or more answers that apply to you.</EM>
<P>
<STRONG>1. On which mountain range(s) or massif(s) do you work? (please type names separated by commas):</STRONG>
