<H3>The Mountain Forum Logo Contest Winner</H3><P>
The Mountain Forum congratulates Ben Wang, winner of the Mountain Forum logo contest.   The winning design, decided by a simple majority vote of participating Forum members, will serve as the official Mountain Forum logo. <P>Thank you, Ben, and Congratulations!<P><P>
<CENTER>
<IMG SRC="bw-color.gif" alt="Logo Winner"border="1"></CENTER>
<BR>
<P>
<P>

A big thank you to all those who contributed designs. If you wish to know the exact vote count, send us an email at <A HREF="mailto:CPoulson@mountain.org">CPoulson@mountain.org</A><P>


<P>

<P>

<IMG SRC=/mtnforum/images/mtnwhatsnew.jpg>
