Date: Mon, 14 Oct 1996 00:47:19 -0700<BR>
From: mleyeh@violet.berkeley.edu<P>
Hi,<P>
I'm a PhD student at the Energy and Resources Group, UC Berkeley. I'm
interested in natural resource management and meeting rural energy
needs in mountainous areas, particularly in Tibetan areas of the PRC.
I'm interested in finding out what the current debates are; and also
just getting  a better grasp on who is doing what work, where (since
this is all kind of new to me) <BR>
-emily yeh<P>


