<h3>  <a href="http://www.realaudio.com"><img vsize="37" hsize="37" align=left src="raudio.jpg"> What is RealAudio?</a> <Font size="-1"><I>RealAudio</I> is an audio delivery system that allows you to hear sound in real time. That's right "audio on demand"!  No more waiting exorbitant time to download files before being able to hear lectures, music, news broadcasts, or even.... messages and important announcements for people.  A 5-minute newscast used to take 25, 30 or even 60 minutes or more to download. But with<I> RealAudio</I> it plays as it comes to your computer. <U>This is an exciting breakthrough in audio delivery for the Internet.</Font></h3><p><p><hr>

